examples.en: After a tough battle, they overcame the enemy.
She overcame her own natural reserve.
The team overcame a four-point deficit to win the game.
She overcame a leg injury and is back running again.
She eventually overcame the deprivations of her childhood.
He overcame the obstacles of poverty and neglect.
The invading army easily overcame the town's defences.
The South Africans overcame the odds to beat Australia.
Weariness overcame her after twelve hours and she fell asleep.
The team overcame fierce competition for their place in the finals.
